Valued at <b>87 billion USD</b> in 2023, the <b>Diamond And Gemstone Market</b> size is expected to grow to <b>120 billion USD</b> by 2033, with a CAGR of <b>3.1%</b> from 2024 to 2033. The report comprises various segments and analyzes the trends and factors playing a substantial role in the market.
